service.name: Jobs, Education and Training Child Care Fee Assistance
service.description: Job, Education and Training Child Care Fee Assistance (JETCCFA) provides extra help with the cost of CCB approved care for eligible parents undertaking activities as part of an Employment Pathway Plan to help them enter or re-enter the workforce. JETCCFA covers most of the gap fee after the customer's Child Care Benefit (CCB) fee reduction is applied. JETCCFA is paid to approved child care services, including long day care, family day care, in-home care, outside school hours care, vacation care and some occasional care services.
